
** Init and Starting

  su postgres

  $ initdb
  $ pg_ctl -l logfile start
  $ createdb testhm

** Test Database

  testhm
  
** Interpreter

  su - postgres

  psql testhm

SQL> show data_directory;  
   data_directory    
---------------------
 /var/lib/pgsql/data

